description: The best-selling Caseology Parallax Case, now for iPhone 8 Plus, features the same prized look but with a better design. It incorporates Caseology’s tried-and-true dual layer technology and a newly improved frame with strategic grooves that offer a better hold needed for taking photos, streaming videos and playing games horizontally. The popular geometric design is stylish and functional, giving your phone a distinct look while providing a secure grip through its textured cover. It’s a trifecta of quality, design and protection worth putting on your new phone.Even with the Parallax’s bold design, protection comes first. This dual layer phone case combines the shock absorbing features of TPU & PC material into one surprisingly slim cover for enhanced protection against drops. The raised front lip protects the iPhone 8 Plus display when faced down and keeps the screen free from scratches. The Parallax’s comprehensive design also includes precise cutouts, tactile button covers and camera bezel protection.
